  Widget::set_window(): Increase the ref count of the Gdk::Window.

  * gdk/src/widget.[hg|ccg]: set_window() increases the ref count of the
  Gdk::Window, since gtk_widget_set_window() does not.
  
  Bug #606903 (Hammered)

