	* gtk/src/notebook.hg:
	* gtk/src/textbuffer.ccg:
	* gtk/src/textbuffer.hg:
	* gtk/src/widget.hg: Put anything documented with @deprecated in
	#ifndef GTKMM_DISABLE_DEPRECATED.

