2010-03-23  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@murrayc.com>

    Fix small API problems found by Jonathan Jongsma.

	* tools/extra_defs_gen/generate_defs_gtk.cc: Add ToolPalette, ToolItemGroup,
    OffscreenWindow.
