2007-07-14  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@murrayc.com>

	* tools/extra_defs_gen/generate_defs_gtk.cc: Mention the GtkPrint*
	classes so that signal/property .defs are generated for these.
	* gdk/src/Makefile.am:
